《'''親密束縛'''》（{{lang-en|''Bonding''}}，標題設計寫為{{lang|en|''BONDiNG''}}）是美國[[黑色幽默|黑色幽默]]網路電視劇，於2019年4月24日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]上首映。<ref name="SeriesOrder">{{Cite web|title=Rightor Doyle’s ‘Bonding’ Short-Form Dark Comedy Series Picked Up By Netflix|url=https://deadline.com/2018/12/rightor-doyle-bonding-short-form-series-picked-up-netflix-backspills-1202520388/|accessdate=April 22, 2019|author=Andreeva|date=December 14, 2018|first=Nellie|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226050619/https://deadline.com/2018/12/rightor-doyle-bonding-short-form-series-picked-up-netflix-backspills-1202520388/|dead-url=no}}</ref>由柔伊·萊文（Zoe Levin），布伦丹·斯内尔（Brendan Scannell），米卡·斯托克（Micah Stock），西奥·斯托克曼（Theo Stockman）和達西·卡登（D'Arcy Carden）等人主演。2020年1月16日，宣布續訂第二季，並於2021年1月27日在Netflix上發布。<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Bonding’ Season 2 Coming to Netflix in January 2021|url=https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/news/bonding-season-2-coming-to-netflix-in-january-2021/|date=December 31, 2020|work=What's on Netflix|access-date=2021-02-23|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110192822/https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/news/bonding-season-2-coming-to-netflix-in-january-2021/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據報導，本劇約略基於創作者Rightor Doyle的個人經驗編撰而成。<ref>{{Cite web|title='Bonding': TV Review|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/bonding-review-1203378|accessdate=2019-05-12|date=April 24, 2019|work=The Hollywood Reporter|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812043445/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/bonding-review-1203378|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年7月，本劇在第二季後被取消。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://deadline.com/2021/07/the-crew-country-comfort-mr-iglesias-bonding-canceled-netflix-kevin-james-gabriel-iglesias-rightor-doyle-deals-1234785656/ |title = ‘The Crew’, ‘Country Comfort’, ‘Mr. Iglesias’ & ‘Bonding’ Canceled As Netflix Remains In Business With Kevin James, Gabriel Iglesias & Rightor Doyle |author = Nellie Andreeva |date = 2021-07-02 |publisher = Deadline Hollywood |language = en}}</ref>

== 概要 ==
蒂芙妮（Tiff Chester）（柔伊·萊文飾演）是一名[[心理学|心理系]]的學生，夜裡則擔任{{le|調教師|Dominatrix}}。她拉了高中摯友彼得·戴文（Pete Devin）（Brendan Scannell飾演）來擔任自己的助理，他是名同性戀。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=‘Bonding’ creator dishes on life of sex and dungeons|url=https://nypost.com/2019/04/18/bonding-creator-dishes-on-life-of-sex-and-dungeons/|accessdate=April 22, 2019|author=Sarner|date=April 18, 2019|first=Lauren|work=New York Post|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225140359/https://nypost.com/2019/04/18/bonding-creator-dishes-on-life-of-sex-and-dungeons/|dead-url=no}}</ref>原本有些疏遠的兩個角色在[[曼哈頓|曼哈顿]]重新連結：彼得在這座城市擔任服務生，即便有著舞台恐懼症仍立志成為喜劇演員。 <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/apr/24/bonding-review-learn-how-to-be-a-dominatrix-in-under-three-hours|title=Bonding review – learn how to be a dominatrix (in under three hours)|author=Mangan|first=Lucy|date=2019-04-24|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2019-05-12|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110125747/https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/apr/24/bonding-review-learn-how-to-be-a-dominatrix-in-under-three-hours|dead-url=no}}</ref>蒂芙（Tiff）則在個人生活與學校、工作間掙扎，嘗試尋求平衡。彼得（Pete）在接觸[[虐戀_(性學)|受虐狂]]和性[[虐戀_(性學)|虐待]]（[[BDSM|BDSM]]）後，這一切逐步幫助他從生活中獲得解放。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Bonding on Netflix release date: How many episodes are in Bonding?|url=https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/1118232/Bonding-Netflix-release-date-How-many-episodes-Bonding-series-episode-lengths|accessdate=2019-05-12|author=Debnath|date=2019-04-24|first=Neela|work=Express.co.uk|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203232528/https://www.express.co.uk/showbiz/tv-radio/1118232/Bonding-Netflix-release-date-How-many-episodes-Bonding-series-episode-lengths|dead-url=no}}</ref>

